msgid ""
"**Charge.** If the boar moves at least 20 feet straight toward a target and "
"then hits it with a tusk attack on the same turn, the target takes an extra "
"7 (2d6) slashing damage. If the target is a creature, it must succeed on a "
"DC 13 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone.    \n"
"**Relentless (Recharges after a Short or Long Rest).** If the boar takes 10 "
"damage or less that would reduce it to 0 hit points, it is reduced to 1 hit "
"point instead. \n"
msgstr ""

